The x3270 Wish List

Here is a list of some of the more interesting suggestions and requests made
for x3270. You may also take this as a list of functions that are definitely
not in this version of x3270.

There is no guarantee that anyone is actively working on these, but feel free
to yourself...

   *  Support for the rest of the extended attributes: field outlining,
     extended validation, etc.
   *  Support for GDDM bit-mapped graphics.
   *  Printer support, i.e., telling the host there is a printer attached to
     your 3270 and doing something intelligent with the output.
   *  Data-entry assists like local columnar tabs, automatic line wrap, etc.
   *  Support for the TN3270E protocol.
